snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade - Season VI: Scourge of Winter (Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
As a wicked army scours the northern lands, warlords from across the known world must unite if they’re to survive the winter. Ride out and purge the land of evil in Season VI: Scourge of Winter, coming to Conqueror’s Blade on December 21!
Players in North America can also start Season VI on brand-new East and West Coast US servers, launching December 16.
Read more: https://conqblade.com/news/652
